    <b>Example:</b><br/>
    <pre><code class="language-bash">
      curl --user gooble:gobble -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"account_name":"abc","bot_name":"xyz", "platform": "facebook", "user_id":"abc123"}' http://ec2-54-208-153-78.compute-1.amazonaws.com/user_blacklists/drop_user.json
    </code></pre>
  </div>
